item.title: Project Galaxy– A remake of 377 cache
item.dc:creator: @TheCyberMan TheCyberMan
item.description:
@TheCyberMan wrote:

Remember modelers, the designs do not need to be intricate. Considering we’re remaking the cache, I think it’s fine to start with more basic models Also, do your best to design some new models that Jagex hasn’t made for RS yet. For example, why not make a saber (maybe even a light saber :P)? You could still have the basic things like plate body, scimitars, helmets, etc. Just make a completely new item every once and awhile Good luck.

Make sure to post your updates here so I can update your status.

Read full topic
